 BUILD ENV
 ############################


 prerequisites 
 =============

 Sometimes it is necessary to install base utils
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 | $ sudo apt-get install build-essential autconf make 			|
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 for vim, vifm, mc use ncurses lib
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 | $ sudo apt-get install libncursesw5-dev				|
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 sometimes it is necceary to install cmake
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 | $ sudo apt-get install cmake						|
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------ 